{"tid":464132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊APPLE嘅巴打請入","createTime":"2017-11-10T08:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T11:23:54.000Z","uid":16941,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d55a4bf863029643282a669fea8ae2a8d847410","tid":464132,"uid":16941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:33:44.000Z","msg":"小弟想搵你地做個訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為final year project 嘅題目係貴公司<br />\n希望你可以幫幫手比少少時間我地 同我地做個訪問<br />\n我知會冇啦啦晒左你啲時間 <br />\n但最後一年 最後一份project 影響到我地畢唔畢到業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望有好心巴打可以同我地做個訪問<br />\n可以係電話做又得 見面做又得(最好)<br />\n<br />\n題目係 調查 點解apple 員工嘅工作滿意度比其他公司高 點解咁多人想得到呢份工<br />\n<br />\n利申 讀緊HR"},{"pid":"c869154dbaf73685f1062eb2310526ee387ad3bc","tid":464132,"uid":16941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:39:52.000Z","msg":"做完個訪問 <br />\n你想點就點啦<br />\n求幫個手 可以唔出名 唔錄片<br />\n淨係求個訪問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搵左好耐都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622bc68106ca4b596a8a2ebccd37508f2cac085f","tid":464132,"uid":16941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36b8c322eced64dc4b1b79640da2f8e6f0377bbc","tid":464132,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:43:37.000Z","msg":"冇錢學人做research <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9c7c1de53db44bb40c129b3805cb9bfe4edaf5","tid":464132,"uid":87973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:43:50.000Z","msg":"無錢賺既野 藍精靈唔會做"},{"pid":"cbe8aa6255f652dfdc053fd8e2098304beb4984e","tid":464132,"uid":16941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:5